  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13081638/adobestock_182043251-1.jpeg" alt="Ski Inclusive" data-udi="media/13081638/adobestock_182043251-1.jpeg" />
<p>Ski Inclusive holidays offer great savings as well as the ultimate in convenience, maximum value and the reassurance of being able to budget for everything you need before your travel for your ski holiday in advance. In many cases, further features such as free bar drinks and children's clubs not to mention a wide range of leisure facilities are included in selected hotels.</p>
<p>Our Ski Inclusive holidays include all of the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Return flights &amp; transfers to resort</strong></li>
<li><strong>7 nights accommodation</strong></li>
<li><strong>7 night meals* on with breakfast, lunch and dinner</strong></li>
<li><strong>Free drinks with dinner</strong></li>
<li><strong>Lift pass included</strong></li>
<li><strong>Ski &amp; boot Hire included</strong></li>
<li><strong>Locations close to the slopes</strong></li>
<li><strong>Value for money</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>*Inclusions vary by hotel. See accommodation details below.</p>
<p><br />Choose from the Inghams Ski Inclusive properties below for outstanding value and fantastic savings!</p>
</div>
<h2><a name="backtotop"></a>Ski Inclusive Accommodation</h2>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1}" title="Hotel Princesa Parc &amp; Spa"><img src="/media/13068681/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-princesa-parc-spa-arinsal.jpeg" alt="Princesa Parc Arinsal" data-udi="umb://media/aaa387cf07c948628fdc0c94ac0f98a2" /></a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1}" title="Hotel Princesa Parc &amp; Spa"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Princesa Parc &amp; Spa - Arinsal</span></a></p>
<p>This resort hotel is just 5 minutes' walk to the gondola and offers excellent facilities including a Wellness Spa and free drinks from the Club Menu.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1}" title="Hotel Princesa Parc &amp; Spa">More information &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><img src="/media/13068684/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-village-club-du-soleil-montgenevre.jpg" alt="VCS Montgenevre" data-udi="umb://media/00e482ff92714ab68696fbba32889377" /></a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Village Club Du Soleil - Montgenevre, France</span></a></p>
<p><span>Nestled on the border with Italy, the Montquitaine chairlift just 150m from the property, providing incredible access to the ski area...</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880}" title="Village Club du Soleil">More information &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><img src="/media/13068686/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-village-club-du-soleil-morzine.jpg" alt="VCU Morzine" data-udi="umb://media/d02becb577be49c0b6070f93851d1da5" /></a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Village Club Du Soleil - Morzine, France</span></a></p>
<p>An ideal choice for keen skiers and families alike. It has a great location with skiing from the Pleney piste and benefits from a sauna, steam room and whirlpool.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a}" title="Village Club du Soleil">More information &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><img src="/media/13068683/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-village-club-du-soleil-les-menuires.jpg" alt="VCS Les Menuires" data-udi="umb://media/7b62d25249b9424da80acc38881d535a" /></a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Village Club Du Soleil - Les Menuires, France</span></a></p>
<p><span>Stunning views can be enjoyed from the sun terrace or relax with a drink in the lounge after a long day on the slopes...</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1}" title="Village Club du Soleil">More information &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952}" title="Hotel Le Mottaret"><img src="/media/13068680/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-mottaret-meribel.jpg" alt="Le Mottaret Meribel" data-udi="umb://media/b75504981af24fb9b78034fe730609bd" /></a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952}" title="Hotel Le Mottaret"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Le Mottaret - Meribel, France</span></a></p>
<p><span>Situated on the side of the piste in Méribel Mottaret 1800, the superb ski-inclusive Hotel Le Mottaret has everything you need</span>.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952}" title="Hotel Le Mottaret">More information &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f}" title="Diana Parc &amp; Spa Hotel"><img src="/media/13068679/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-diana-parc-spa-arinsal.jpg" alt="Diana Parc Arinsal" data-udi="umb://media/7906dd1c255c4b8b9be15a6fb917e170" /></a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f}" title="Diana Parc &amp; Spa Hotel"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Diana Parc &amp; Spa - Arinsal</span></a></p>
<p><span>This luxury resort hotel is Arinsal’s flagship property, offering excellent facilities with free drinks and meals in the Louis XV restaurant and drinks in the Aquarium Cocktail Bar.</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f}" title="Diana Parc &amp; Spa Hotel">More information &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/6f8f5deb3e8a4fd284b0bcae7ae10c23" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6f8f5deb3e8a4fd284b0bcae7ae10c23}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><img src="/media/13068337/_dsc6407-13.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/b3f4f18d004446029f1fbb3a3bd43e05" /></a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/6f8f5deb3e8a4fd284b0bcae7ae10c23" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6f8f5deb3e8a4fd284b0bcae7ae10c23}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Village Club Du Soleil - Les Deux Alpes</span></a></p>
<p><span>A ski-in/ski-out ski inclusive hotel with a range of children's clubs.</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/6f8f5deb3e8a4fd284b0bcae7ae10c23" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6f8f5deb3e8a4fd284b0bcae7ae10c23}" title="Village Club du Soleil">More information &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 70px;">
<p><strong>Prefer a more flexible catering option but looking for discounted ski equipment and lift pass? Why not choose our <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/ski-inclusive-bundles" target="_blank" title="Ski inclusive ski bundles">Ski Bundle</a> offer where you can save up to £128 per person.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-types/ski-inclusive-holidays#backtotop">Back to top</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>]]></bodyText>
